Package org.htwk.graphplot.expression

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FunctionInformation.ParameterCountCheck  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassEnumerator
    This class provides static functions which can be used to scan a specified package and receive all the contained classes.
    ExpressionInterpreter
    This is a factory class for expressions.
    FunctionInformation
    This class is supposed to hold information about an interpretable function.
    OperationInformation
    This class is supposed to hold information about an interpretable operation.
    StringTransformer
    This class shall help to perform basic string transformations in order to create a standardized string format for a correct interpretation of the string as expression.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidExpressionException
    This exception describes problems with a given string which should represent an expression but can somehow not be transformed.
    InvalidFunctionParamException
    This exception describes problems when the given parameters for a function does not match its definition.
    InvalidVariableNameException
    This exception describes problems when variable names are used which are not declared.
